# Engineer Modifications

The following Engineer Modifications are presented in alphabetical order for use with an Engineer's *Infuse Items* feature.

# Modified Defense
**Prerequisite:* 5th level Engineer*
**Required Item: A mundane suit of armor or shield*

A creature gains a +1 bonus to Armor Class while wearing (armor) or wielding (shield) this modified item.

This bonus increases to +2 at 9th level and +3 at 13th level. If the modified item already has an Item Modification installed that increases Armor Class, your bonus to AC cannot exceed +3.

# Modified Weapon
**Prerequisite:* 5th level Engineer*
**Required Item: A mundane suit of armor or shield*

This enhanced weapon grants a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it.

This bonus increases to +2 at 9th level and +3 at 13th level. If the modified item already has an Item Modification installed that increases ARMOR CLASS, your bonus to AC cannot exceed +3.
